msgid "## 1. 函数概述"
msgstr "## 1. Function Overview"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Math_Ops/log.md:4
msgid "简介：该函数用于计算x的逐元素自然对数。"
msgstr "Introduction: This function is used to compute the element-wise natural logarithm of x."

#. type: code
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Math_Ops/log.md:6
msgid ""
"```python\n"
"triton.language.log(x, _semantic=None)\n"
"```\n"
msgstr ""

